lead_paragraph: China will host a Union Cycliste Internationale (UCI) world tour cycling race starting in 2017, Dalian Wanda Group said on Thursday in a press release.

headline.print_headline: China to Host UCI World Tour Cycling Race Starting in 2017: Wanda Group
